Happiness Scores¶

Computing average happiness scores of a text T: $$ h_{\mathrm{avg}}(T)=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{N} h_{\mathrm{avg}}\left(w_{i}\right) f_{i}}{\sum_{i=1}^{N} f_{i}}=\sum_{i=1}^{N} h_{\mathrm{avg}}\left(w_{i}\right) p_{i} $$

In [ ]:
labMT_data = pd.read_csv("../data/Hedonometer.csv")
In [ ]:
lab_dict = dict(zip(labMT_data.Word, labMT_data["Happiness Score"]))

    def get_avg_score(doc):
        available_words = [w for w in doc if w in lab_dict.keys()]
        word_frequencies = nltk.FreqDist(available_words)
        total_frequency = len(available_words)
        
        total = 0
        
        for word, weight in word_frequencies.items():
            total += lab_dict[word] * weight
        
        return round(total/total_frequency,4)

WordShift Graphs¶

In [ ]:
def find_geo_and_proper_nouns(text_list):
        geotext = GeoText()

        input_list = text_list
        input_text = ','.join(input_list) 

        geo_extractions = geotext.extract(input_text=input_text, span_info=False)
        geo_to_remove = list(geo_extractions['cities'].keys()) + list(geo_extractions['countries'].keys())

        tagged_text = pos_tag(input_list)
        proper_nouns_to_remove = [word for (word, tag) in tagged_text if tag=='NNP' or tag=='NNPS']

        words_to_remove = geo_to_remove + proper_nouns_to_remove

        return words_to_remove
